quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  42,23,"Ko Й—um woni ko Allah wewlinirta jeyaaЙ“e Makko gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Й“e golli golle moЖґЖґe. Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di e Й—um, si wanaa tun giggol enЙ—am Й—am\". Kala faggitiiЙ—o moЖґЖґere, Men Й“eydanay mo moЖґЖґere e hoore mayre. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, mantoowo"
  42,24,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay o fefindor nde e hoore Allah fenaande. Si Allah haajuno, O notayno e Й“ernda maa nden. Alla no meha meere nden, O tabintinira goonga kan Daalol Makko ngol. Pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o gunndooji Й“erЙ—e Й—en"
  42,25,"Ko Kanko woni jaЙ“anoowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en tuubuubuyee, O yaafoo bonЙ—i Й—in, e hoore Himo anndi ko golloton kon"
  42,26,"Himo jaabinana gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Й“e golli moЖґЖґuЙ—i, O Й“eydana Й“e e Й“ural Makko ngal. HeeferЙ“e Й“en non, hino woodani Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah yaГ±Г±anno jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en [fow] arsike, pellet, Й“e bewayno ka leydi; kono Himo jippinira emmbere ko O muuyi. Pellet, ko O HummpitiiЙ—o, yi*oowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  42,28,"Ko Kano woni jippinoowo toЙ“o ngon Й“aawo Й“e taЖґaade, O saaka yurmeende Makko nden. Ko Kanko kadi woni GiЙ—o, YettiniiЙ—o On"
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e ruugayЙ—i Й—i O saaki Й—in hakkunde majji. Kanko e fii mooЙ“indiroygol Й“e ngol, si O haajii, ko O hattanЙ—o"
  42,30,"Kala ko heЙ“i on e masiibo, ko sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—en faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non, ko Й—uuЙ—i"
  42,31,"On wonaali laawotooЙ“e ka leydi ; alanaa on gaanin Allah, giЙ—o, wanaa ballo"
